    "description_long": "This object is a standard rectangular speed limit sign displaying 'SPEED LIMIT 20' in bold black letters and numbers on a white background. The sign is mounted on a tall, slender, black pole that appears to be made of metal. The sign face is bordered by a thin black outline, enhancing its visibility. The back of the sign is plain and unmarked, with a smooth metallic finish. The pole is straight and cylindrical, with no decorative features or additional attachments. This type of sign is commonly found in urban environments to indicate a maximum speed of 20 kilometers per hour for vehicles.",
